                        <li>The Federal Government's intervention shall provide assistance to the States and Local Governments in Nigeria for the purposes of uniform and qualitative basic education throughout Nigeria. </li>
                        <li>Every Government in Nigeria shall provide free, compulsory and universal basic education for every child of primary and junior secondary school age. </li>
                        
                    </ul>
                   
                    <a class="button" href="#" role="button">Read More</a>
                </div>
